8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Hive and Reclaim AI share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Collaboration. Where Hive pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Notes and Templates, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Hive holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Reclaim AI scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Hive and Reclaim AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Hive's free tier and Reclaim AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
